A '''taxi speeder''', also known as a '''hovertaxi''', '''hover cab''', '''grav-cab''', '''repulsorcab''',{{Fact}} or '''repulsortaxi'''<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref> was the name applied to [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeders]] that functioned as taxis. Unlike their [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]] counterparts, [[Air taxi/Legends|air taxis]], taxi speeders operated close to the ground. Some versions were piloted by [[Droid/Legends|droids]].

